{
  "texts": [
    "This approach aims to extract latent information in such heterogeneous topologies.",
    "55 proposed the MHTAN-DTI method, which, compared to other GNN-based approaches, enhances the capture of higher-order structural and semantic information in biological heterogeneous graphs through meta-path expansion.",
    "This method leverages a hierarchical transformer structure to model contextual information, assigns weights to different meta-paths, introduces an attention network for weighted fusion, distinguishes the importance of different meta-paths, reduces the impact of noisy data on the model, and improves model robustness.",
    "Chen et al.",
    "introduced the SDGAE method, a graph convolutional autoencoder approach 56."
  ]
}